name: BOB on Genify
description: The 1st Generative Inscription curated by Genify."BOB: BlockOnBlock" is a striking generative art masterpiece that pays tribute to Georges Seurat's pointillism, a cornerstone of Impressionism. This digital creation, skillfully crafted using p5.js, stands as a contemporary ode to Seurat's influential legacy. The piece uniquely blends the concept of blocks, suggestive of both digital pixels and blockchain, with the pointillist technique, forming a bridge between traditional art and modern technology.
